description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Sensory Overload is an experimental game, from a new suite of developers, exploring the sensation of flying in near blindness, with only a small headlight, and music, to tell you what's going to come at you next.
